/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-013/receptionist-log.md:4:- Inspected the step-013 goal and reasoning, run-009 winning/refined chain files, step-009 endpoint freeze results, step-010 prior-art overlap screen, step-011 prior-art screen, step-012 endpoint and solution-class admission, and the frozen solution-class / localization / obstruction-screening factual files.
