+# Exploration 003 Report
+
+## Goal
+
+Freeze the anti-repackaging and prior-art gate for the active reformulation audit, then decide whether the branch has earned continuation into Chain Step 2.
+
+## Method
+
+- Read the files named in `GOAL.md` for this exploration.
+- Read the step-level calibration prompt in `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-013/GOAL.md` and the strategist split in `REASONING.md`.
+- Pulled the inherited endpoint, burden, solution-class, and localization freezes from earlier exact-rewrite and endpoint-admission records so the anti-repackaging rule could be written in the branch's actual burden currency.
+
+## Sources Consulted
+
+- [VERIFIED] `GOAL.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-013/GOAL.md`
