+
+## Findings
+
+### Initial setup
+
+- [VERIFIED] Report skeleton created in the exploration workdir before substantive analysis.
+
+### 1. The burden currency is already concrete enough to support a real anti-repackaging gate
+
+- [VERIFIED] The active branch is not operating in free-floating stylistic language. The inherited interface is already frozen as:
+  - solution class:
+    suitable weak solutions in the Leray-Hopf energy class with LEI;
+  - endpoint family on the inherited floor:
+    CKN/Lin-style local concentration exclusion / endpoint-regularity exclusion;
+  - audit architecture:
+    local-energy flux/localization;
+  - fixed bad term:
+    `I_flux[phi] = ∬_{Q_r} (|u|^2 + 2p) u · ∇phi`;
+  - gain currency:
+    smaller effective cost on that same localized LEI cutoff-flux bundle under the same protocol;
+  - localization regime:
+    one CKN-style parabolic cylinder with one shared smooth cutoff and explicit charging of projection, Calderon-Zygmund, Biot-Savart, commutator, and reconstruction debt.
+- [VERIFIED] `CHAIN.md` and `run-009/winning-chain.md` require the anti-repackaging and prior-art screens to be written in this same ledger, not in candidate-native language.
+- [INFERRED] That means the anti-repackaging classifier can now be made mechanical:
+  the question is whether a packet changes the theorem-facing LEI/CKN burden after all named debt is restored, not whether the packet has a novel identity, a named observable, or elegant packaging.
+
+### 2. Family labels must collapse before the equivalence screen
+
+- [VERIFIED] The repository already provides the meta rule:
+  collapse family labels first, then run equivalent-packaging screening on the smallest honest family menu.
+- [VERIFIED] For this branch, labels such as alignment, eigenframe, restricted-Euler, back-to-label, circulation, or other slogan-level mechanism names do not create distinct live families unless they already cash out as an estimate-level action on the frozen burden.
+- [INFERRED] Operationally, a later packet does not escape the equivalence screen by renaming one known exact rewrite, isolating one sub-observable inside it, or describing the same transport/projection/localization interaction in a different variable.
+
+### 3. Exact three-way anti-repackaging classifier
+
+- [PROPOSED] Use the following exact classifier for Chain Step 2 and Step 3 packets.
+
+#### `equivalent redistribution`
+
+- [VERIFIED] Classify a packet as `equivalent redistribution` if, after family-label collapse and full debt charging, its usable content is only a redistribution of the already frozen LEI cutoff-flux burden.
+- [VERIFIED] The bucket includes all of the following:
+  - expectation-free or deterministic exact rewrite that merely shifts cost between the cubic and pressure pieces of `I_flux[phi]`;
+  - a localization, filtration, stopping, projection, Biot-Savart, or reconstruction maneuver whose apparent gain disappears when the associated debt is charged;
+  - a package whose only theorem-facing consequence is the same effective localized LEI inequality with no smaller coefficient, no weaker same-scheme hypothesis, and no new transfer lemma;
+  - a packet absorbed by an already known reformulation neighborhood because the claimed novelty is only a repackaging of exactness, bookkeeping, or variable choice.
+- [INFERRED] Screening consequence:
+  reject immediately for identity-level redistribution or prior-art absorption.
+
+#### `ambiguous redistribution`
+
+- [VERIFIED] Classify a packet as `ambiguous redistribution` if it names a concrete place where the frozen burden might change, but the packet does not yet exhibit a demonstrated theorem-facing delta after debt is charged.
+- [VERIFIED] This bucket is the only allowed holding pen for packets whose current content is stronger than slogan-level packaging but weaker than a live mechanism change.
+- [PROPOSED] Minimum conditions for this label:
+  - one exact insertion point on the frozen ledger is named:
+    a specific slot in the localized `I_flux[phi]` estimate, or one allowed cross-currency column with a named transfer target;
+  - the packet states one exact prior-art comparator and one exact mathematical delta it hopes to realize;
+  - the packet does not yet prove the delta survives localization, projection/pressure recovery, admissibility, and endpoint exchange.
+- [INFERRED] Screening consequence:
+  keep alive only provisionally, and only if the packet identifies the exact unresolved place where the baseline burden might move. Otherwise demote to `equivalent redistribution`.
+
+#### `potentially live mechanism change`
+
+- [VERIFIED] Classify a packet as `potentially live mechanism change` only if the claimed novelty already acts in the frozen burden ledger rather than in candidate-native language.
+- [PROPOSED] Minimum conditions for this label:
+  - same-currency case:
+    the packet states an exact prototype inequality, localized identity, or coefficient comparison showing a smaller effective cost on the same `I_flux[phi]` bundle under the same solution class and cutoff protocol;
+  - cross-currency case:
+    the packet states an exact gain in one allowed ledger currency and also names the transfer lemma required to cash that gain out as the theorem-facing LEI improvement;
+  - the claimed gain survives explicit charging of localization, pressure recovery, projection/Biot-Savart, commutator, reconstruction, admissibility, and prior-art overlap debt;
+  - the packet's delta is not already absorbed by the closest known reformulation.
+- [INFERRED] Screening consequence:
+  admit to the later bottleneck sheet, but only with the exact delta and debt ledger attached.
+
+### 4. Minimum evidence required to avoid immediate prior-art absorption
+
+- [PROPOSED] A later candidate packet is absorbed immediately unless it supplies all of the following minimum evidence.
+
+1. [VERIFIED] One nearest-prior-art comparator by exact package name, not just a family slogan.
+2. [VERIFIED] One exact shared mathematical core with that comparator:
+   what identity, representation, localization protocol, or solution-class content is already standard.
+3. [VERIFIED] One exact claimed delta written in the frozen burden currency:
+   either
+   - smaller effective coefficient on `I_flux[phi]`,
+   - a strictly weaker hypothesis in the same localized LEI closure scheme,
+   - or one allowed cross-currency gain plus a named transfer lemma back to the LEI burden.
+4. [VERIFIED] One debt ledger showing where localization, pressure recovery, projection/Biot-Savart, commutator, reconstruction, admissibility, and endpoint-exchange costs are charged.
+5. [VERIFIED] One explicit statement that the packet stays inside the fixed solution class and CKN-style cutoff protocol.
+
+- [INFERRED] If any one of these items is missing, the honest default is prior-art absorption or equivalent redistribution rather than "needs more exploration."
+- [INFERRED] This minimum-evidence rule is stricter than merely naming a new observable or a different variable. That is necessary because Step-012 already recorded that comparator naming without a theorem-facing delta is too weak to expose absorbed reformulations.
+
+### 5. Nearest-prior-art audit format
+
+- [PROPOSED] Later candidate packets should include one `nearest-prior-art card` with the following fixed fields.
+
+| field | required content |
+| --- | --- |
+| `candidate family after label collapse` | the smallest honest package name after removing slogan aliases |
+| `closest known reformulation` | exact known comparator name or neighborhood |
+| `shared content already standard` | the exact identity / representation / localized bookkeeping already present in the comparator |
+| `claimed mathematical delta` | exact theorem-facing delta in the frozen burden currency |
+| `delta type` | `same-currency` or `cross-currency with transfer lemma` |
+| `required transfer lemma` | exact lemma name if the delta is not already a direct LEI coefficient gain |
+| `debt ledger` | localization, pressure, projection/Biot-Savart, commutator, reconstruction, admissibility, endpoint exchange |
+| `anti-repackaging classification` | one of the three frozen labels |
+| `absorption verdict` | `absorbed`, `ambiguous`, or `not absorbed on current record` |
+
+- [INFERRED] The card is deliberately narrow.
+  It forces the packet to name the closest known reformulation and an exact mathematical delta before any descriptive mechanism story is allowed to count.
+
+### 6. Closest currently known baselines on the repository record
+
+- [VERIFIED] For the stochastic-style prior-art warning carried over from Step-012, the closest named baseline on disk is the `Constantin-Iyer` / stochastic circulation / backward-flow neighborhood, with exact reformulation and expectation/localization bookkeeping already treated as common terrain and strategically insufficient.
+- [VERIFIED] For the active exact-rewrite audit, the repository already froze the standard exact-rewrite shortlist:
+  `divergence / stress form`,
+  `Lamb-vector / Helmholtz-projected form`,
+  and
+  `vorticity transport / Biot-Savart form`.
+- [VERIFIED] Step-006 already judged that exact identity-level leverage from those packages does not by itself survive the Tao screen as theorem-facing leverage on the fixed `I_flux[phi]` burden.
+- [INFERRED] So the current gate does not need to rediscover a comparator universe.
+  It needs to force every later packet to say exactly which known neighborhood it is beating and exactly where the burden changes in the frozen ledger.
+
+### 7. Is the scope lock concrete enough to proceed?
+
+- [VERIFIED] The endpoint window is concrete enough:
+  the only locally frozen theorem-facing floor is the suitable-weak / Leray-Hopf plus LEI package, and the primary endpoint family on that floor is local concentration exclusion / CKN-Lin endpoint-regularity exclusion.
+- [INFERRED] The honest backup endpoint family is the continuation-style reserve already described in the inherited record:
+  only if a candidate behaves like near-coercive norm control, not as a parallel open menu.
+- [VERIFIED] The burden ledger is concrete enough for later packet screening because the bad term, gain currency, same-protocol rule, and disqualifying architecture changes are already frozen in the repository.
+- [VERIFIED] The solution class and localization regime are concrete enough because the fixed suitable-weak / LEI class and one shared CKN-style parabolic cutoff protocol are already specified at the right level of detail for candidate-localized equation work.
+- [INFERRED] The unresolved issue from Step-012 was not lack of burden currency. It was lack of a theorem-facing comparator packet. The present exploration fixes the screening format for that exact gap.
+
+## Failed Attempts / Dead Ends
+
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-013/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md` is still only a skeleton, so I could not inherit a finished sibling memo for the burden-ledger freeze and had to synthesize directly from the underlying library and prior-step records.
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-012-exploration-002-prior-art-and-anti-repackaging.md` confirms that the repository never turned the `Constantin-Iyer` neighborhood into a fully theorem-facing comparator memo.
+- [INFERRED] That gap is real, but it does not force a Step-013 failure here because the current task is to freeze the gate format and screening threshold, not to prove one candidate already clears it.
+
+## Verdict
+
+- [INFERRED] Final verdict:
+  `scope lock passed, proceed to candidate slate and localized equation audit`
+- [INFERRED] What is now frozen for Chain Step 2:
+  - primary endpoint family:
+    CKN/Lin-style local concentration exclusion on the inherited LEI floor;
+  - backup endpoint family:
+    continuation-style reserve only if a candidate already behaves like near-coercive norm control;
+  - theorem-facing burden:
+    the fixed localized LEI cutoff-flux bundle `I_flux[phi]`;
+  - admissible gain notion:
+    smaller effective LEI cutoff-flux cost in the same protocol, or an allowed cross-currency gain with an explicit transfer lemma;
+  - solution class:
+    suitable weak solutions in the Leray-Hopf energy class with LEI;
+  - localization regime:
+    one shared CKN-style parabolic cylinder and smooth cutoff with all nonlocal and commutator debt charged in that same package;
+  - anti-repackaging gate:
+    the three-way classifier frozen above;
+  - prior-art gate:
+    the minimum-evidence rule and nearest-prior-art card frozen above.
+- [INFERRED] This is precise enough for Step 2 because later candidate packets can now be killed quickly for:
+  identity-level redistribution,
+  absorbed prior art,
+  unpriced cross-currency narration,
+  or architecture-changing pseudo-gains.

